#
"AIRY WATER" Spell.
 
Area of effect: room Aggressive:  No Cumulative:  N/A Duration:  
Dependent on proficiency of caster Type of spell:  Enchantment
 
"Airy Water" causes a bubble of breathable air to expand forth from the
caster when he is submerged in a large body of water, making verbal
communication and regular breathing possible. 
